{"tid":325086,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝攝錄機拍得女宿生裸體    美國出世港大精算系高材生偷拍判感化","createTime":"2017-07-17T03:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T11:49:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"facec967c15010d3a6d4257f5bc18c9ca57a99de","tid":325086,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170717/large/1500260525_9c66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170717%2Flarge%2F1500260525_9c66.jpg&h=a6c0ef9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於DSE以優異成績取得獎學金入讀港大精算系的高材生，去年7月潛入女宿友房中放置攝錄機偷拍對方，被揭發後承認之前亦曾兩度偷拍，警方隨後在其電腦發現多段他偷拍得來的女生裸體片段。高材生早前承認三項不誠實取用電腦罪，裁判官鑑於高材生年輕，得到家人的支持，相信本案是單獨事件，被告應不會再犯，今判被告接受感化18個月，另須付500元堂費。<br />\n<br />\n辯方為被告夏健祺（21歲）求情時指出，被告早已接受心理輔導，他獲建議守感化或社會服務令，他願意守感化，雙親亦認為他較適合接受感化令監管，望裁判官給他一個機會。<br />\n<br />\n被告早前向律政司要求簽保守行為，但沒被接納，辯方早前透露被告父親是公務員，母親任行政助理，被告於美國出生，畢業於培正中學。"},{"pid":"b647ae653c78d2040d631e0ef13af315be8a9d84","tid":325086,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da3b88df166c3567085f8074ee13a8c70216a40","tid":325086,"uid":49065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faca761f95e65d1493328a90bc57dd5cd500ff96","tid":325086,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:22:32.000Z","msg":"咁就一世"},{"pid":"3d19c8e9d747057060f079a319efc58dcb95f79e","tid":325086,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"美國出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11379e6c2cfc32dae8b997b85de66d65d40af4bc","tid":325086,"uid":119591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"rep